{"tid":2409881,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日本人氣女聲優自爆參拜靖國神社　遭陸網友批「辱華」揚言抵制！","createTime":"2021-02-16T07:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T11:39:17.000Z","uid":16659,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e474a519d90272aaa94c8a4ed928d230cbdf711a","tid":2409881,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:14:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5454/5454940.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5454%2F5454940.jpg&h=b60f389c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾出演《未聞花名》、《罪惡王冠》、《ReLIFE》等作品的日本知名女聲優茅野愛衣11日因前往奉有日本甲級戰犯的「靖國神社」參拜，遭到大陸網友撻伐，認為她「辱華」。茅野愛衣當天在廣播節目中提到此事，隨後便引發喧然大波，如今事件越演越烈，該期節目的影片也緊急從Youtube下架。事實上，茅野先前就曾因來台參加動漫節時稱「台灣是一個很親切的國家」，而遭到對岸網友砲轟。<br />\n<br />\n女聲優茅野愛衣11日在廣播節目「茅野愛衣のむすんでひらいて」中提到，自己當天先去參拜了靖國神社，然而靖國神社因奉入日本甲級戰犯，因此經常在日本國內與國際社會引發爭議，就連日本首相也幾乎不敢在任內參拜。儘管茅野愛衣身分不像政治人物一般特殊敏感，但仍然因此遭到大陸網友砲轟。<br />\n<br />\n茅野愛衣在節目中也稱，靖國神社是個讓人心曠神怡的好地方，再度引發大陸網友不滿，甚至揚言發起抵制。事件持續燃燒，儘管茅野愛衣已經在Youtube下架該期節目，但大陸網友已開始要求Bilibili（影音平台）下架與她相關的作品。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5454/5454942.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5454%2F5454942.jpg&h=f42a3fe1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲提到參拜靖國神社的第152期節目已被下架。（圖／茅野愛衣 10th Anniversary Channel）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n茅野愛衣出道至今已11年，期間替多部動畫配音，曾出演《怪物王女》、《未聞花名》、罪惡王冠》、《冰菓》、《櫻花莊的寵物女孩》、《我女友與青梅竹馬的慘烈修羅場》、《NO GAME NO LIFE 遊戲人生》、《不起眼女主角培育法》、《為美好的世界獻上祝福！》、《ReLIFE》、《齊木楠雄的災難》、《無職轉生：到了異世界就拿出真本事》等多部作品。"},{"pid":"7677829e419265affd3d01cd46baf51aeee1f1e1","tid":2409881,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:17:49.000Z","msg":"以為av 女優，諗住。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f29221c10da61e2950404a743ae5e1cea289abf","tid":2409881,"uid":159697,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:52:24.000Z","msg":"蘇玉華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13b84d9feed034e5c6424d2143f202963c321920","tid":2409881,"uid":21249,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:53:29.000Z","msg":"個個聲優學佢咁，實玩死班支那毒撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236ef1da254177b8b6ec013be7f7d90eaf800c97","tid":2409881,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13b84d9feed034e5c6424d2143f202963c321920","tid":2409881,"uid":21249,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:53:29.000Z","msg":"個個聲優學佢咁，實玩死班支那毒撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:55:26.000Z","msg":"扎砲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e8f350e5bc3b2fabb4ecf71a12b33c90f2f544a","tid":2409881,"uid":3405,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:59:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W9sCH9A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW9sCH9A.png&h=1cbfe518&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0de35b2401a472988fb70362d9ae43e663ae218c","tid":2409881,"uid":18120,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T08:08:14.000Z","msg":"班友又唔買碟嘅，扮乜春大帝呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a74733310e22193afeedc0db6ee765c6ba82ad","tid":2409881,"uid":297306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T11:21:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eadb96cfaa382146cd505700cab5d29b79adea00","tid":2409881,"uid":297306,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T11:23:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f10c717284dda8d4b8fb8b591a914a7cb494a079","tid":2409881,"uid":363436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T11:24:16.000Z","msg":"恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm